{"tid":1315993,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"沙田法院外16男17女被捕","createTime":"2019-07-14T15:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T15:52:37.000Z","uid":135890,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"fc99369811f1c82182e75648b331e6c7772d8353","tid":1315993,"uid":135890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:15:12.000Z","msg":"【即時】(22:55) 約晚上10時40分，在沙田法院外被警方搜身和查身份證的16男17女，全部被警方以非法集結罪拘捕。現場不少警員未有戴上委任證，只有部份警員身上有展示警員編號。10時50分，被捕市民被帶上旅遊巴，前往葵涌警署。有市民向記者表示，今晚是來參加電影放映會。<br />\n<br />\n警員搜查向示威者期間，多次大喝「唔好玩電話」，然後沒收示威者的手機。有一名身穿螢光衣、背有紅十字圖案的男子在警方大聲呼喝後情緒激動，舉高雙手不斷說「阿Sir我唔係」、「唔好打我」，女警安撫近10分鐘後，他仍害怕得無法說出完整句子。<br />\n<br />\n【不斷更新】沙田大遊行現場<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2YUeR2m\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2YUeR2m&d=uli%2BLK8ypwQfiBTSi%2FGP9zcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=3733a9f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2YUeR2m</a><br />\n<br />\n#獨媒報導<br />\n追蹤最新消息：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/inmediahknet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finmediahknet&d=uli%2BLK8ypwQfiBTSi%2FGP9zcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=90168e4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/inmediahknet</a><br />\n報導有價，請月捐支持<br />\n<a href=\"http://inmediahk.net/donate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finmediahk.net%2Fdonate&d=uli%2BLK8ypwQfiBTSi%2FGP9zcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=2e7e961e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Finmediahk.net%2Fdonate&h=5011d3a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">inmediahk.net/donate</a>"},{"pid":"3595672ee80be06172d7a6fd48ef52e97d5961c9","tid":1315993,"uid":199893,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:16:44.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死黑警<br />\n天唔收你 你都會被香港人收你皮"},{"pid":"78d9976416e1c9cb69db6ff323c604cdae5d4b3c","tid":1315993,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:17:18.000Z","msg":"女警安撫近10分鐘後<br />\n安撫?"},{"pid":"5a2f61c16bb3ffef2f1d5cff5e2d3dfec7fca9c2","tid